title: CUOMO OUT, MTN DEW About Nothing  8.11.21

description:
In episode 967, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian Brandie Posey to discuss the Cuomo resigning, Obamas bday party, AOC and CNN, Majorie Taylor Greene being close to a Twitter ban, Mountain Dew with booze in it, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Oh Cuomo resigned…Time’s Up?
  2. Obama Birthday Party
  3. AOC not running against Schumer CNN doesn’t care…
  4. Marjorie Taylor Greene is SOOO CLOSE to getting banned from Twitter
  5. MTN Dew with booze?
  6. Listen: We Are The Union - “Boys Will Be Girls”
